# AI Development Guidelines

## Code Generation
- Generate boilerplate (ViewModels, data classes, modules)
- Create Compose UI layouts with Material 3
- Generate test cases and mock data

## Documentation Requirements
- Add `// AI-generated:` comment for AI-created code blocks
- Document significant AI prompts in commit messages
- Maintain AI usage log in `context/ai-usage.md`

## Review Process
- Verify AI-generated code follows project rules
- Test all AI-generated functionality
- Ensure AI code meets Clean Architecture principles

## Prohibited AI Usage
- Do not use AI for critical business logic without review
- Do not blindly accept AI suggestions for architecture decisions
- Always validate AI-generated dependency configurations

## AI Integration Areas
1. UI component generation
2. Repository implementations  
3. Test case creation
4. Utility function development
5. Documentation writing